# Rust build artifacts
/target/

# wasm-pack output (regenerated by `wasm-pack build`)
/www/pkg/

# Cargo lock is kept for binaries; for libraries it's conventional to omit it,
# but since this is a WASM app (effectively a binary artifact), keep it.
# Cargo.lock  ← intentionally NOT ignored

# wasm-pack may also output here when run from project root
/pkg/

